query:
UPDATE mw_rooms SET
            name = $1,
            password_hash = $2,
            password_salt = $3,
            invites = $4,
            base_queue = $5,
            player_queues = $6,
            created = $7,
            last_saved = $8,
            autodelete_delta = $9,
            allow_send_all = $10,
            metadata = $11
        WHERE id = $12
